List the actual job titles present across the leads currently in the user's selection — the candidate set the user can ask to enrich.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} after leadbay_select_leads, to know which titles are even available before launching a bulk enrichment.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} standalone — the selection must already be populated, otherwise the result is an empty array. leadbay_enrich_titles wraps this whole flow when you don't need to inspect the title list manually.
